questionsAndAnswers.question: Requirements to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First, you will have to purchase a domain & hosting. Feel free to discuss if you haven't purchased yet, I'll guide you. (1) Domain & Hosting with Cpanel (2) Logo (3) Paragraph text for About Us Page (4) List of your services with one to two paragraph about each services (5) Email of Business, Locati

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you show us your Portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Why not. Kindly message me and I'll show you my portfolio and my works

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have Wordpress.com account, is that enough?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sorry, Wordpress.com is different from Wordpress.org. We can only design website on Wordpress.org provided script which will run on a hosting server & you need a hosting server and domain name for that.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I do not have the content for the website, can we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will add dummy content so that you would be able to replace that with your own content in future. The content will be dummy "Lorum Ipsum" and will not be relevant to any industry.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Even if you don't know any programming language, You can easily edit your website. This is the power of wordpress. After watching few tutorials, you can change any thing. I will send the tutorial at the end.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you convert PSD design to WordPress site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, i do. Please message me first with jpg images so that we can discuss and check the design to estimate cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I do not provide domain and hosting. In order to have full control over the website, it is highly recommended that you purchase these yourself in your name. I will recommend your best hosting so you can just ask me in the inbox and I will send you all the steps on how to buy.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide website maintenance in future?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, As I am providing unlimited revision for the website. So in the future, you can also contact me for any maintenance of the website. I will do my mt best for you. My 1st priority to satisfy my clients with quality work & friendly customer support

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my site will be fully Responsive to all devices including mobile and tablet?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, it will be 100% responsive to all media devices.
